        .hero 
          .hero__content
            .hero__title
              h1 Powerful 
                span.hero__title--Powerful SERP Tracker
              p Daily rank updates for all your keywords. Unlimited on-demand checks. Advanced reporting to grow your traffic.
              .hero__title--Explore
                a.hero__title--Explore--backgound Explore Plans
                  <svg class="down-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 3L14 8L8 13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M14 8H2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>
              .hero__title--avatar
                img(src="img/users@2x.webp", alt="", width= "90",height="40")
                span 241,000+ Happy Users
            .hero__desc
              .hero__desc--img
                .hero__desc--img--frame
                  img(src="img/hero@2x.webp", alt="" ,width="1200",height="685")
        .testimonial
          .testimonial__heading
            h2 Our Customers Love Us
            p You're in good company. Here's what our amazing customers </br> have to say about us
            .testimonial__item
              .testimonial__item--avatar
                +testimonial__username(
                    "img/zack@2x.webp",
                    "Zack Notes",
                    "@zacknotes",
                    "i like whatsmyserp. Cheap, great UX and design"
                )
                +testimonial__username(
                  "img/vitorica@2x.webp",
                  "VictoriaSEO",
                  "@VictoriaSEO_",
                  "WhatsMySerp offers rank tracking with unlimited daily refreshes and filtered SERP checking. I'm particularly a fan of the free browser extension, and with the amount of underperforming articles plus keywords I've discovered using it, I didn't mind throwing some $ at it"
                )
              .testimonial__item--avatar
                +testimonial__username(
                  "img/amanda@2x.webp",
                  "Amanda | Poised Avenue Design Studio",
                  "@poisedavenue",
                  "Your website SERPs rank is an important analytic to keep track of. Use http://whatsmyserp.com to get a free overview of your ranking for specific keywords. Which keywords are you landing on page 1 for?"
                )
                +testimonial__username(
                  "img/beau@2x.webp",
                  "Beau Brewer Digital",
                  "@Beau__Brewer",
                  "You're welcome! 👍 Finally, a fairly priced rank and SERP tool! 🏆"
                )
              .testimonial__item--avatar
                +testimonial__username(
                  "img/venkat@2x.webp",
                  "Venkat Randa",
                  "@VenkatRanda",
                  `Best Rank Tracking Tools you use in this 2023 digital era.
                  ... Whatsmyserp
                  > SE Ranking > SiteChecker`
                )
                +testimonial__username(
                    "img/dml@2x.webp",
                    "Digital Marketing Lane 📢",
                    "@DigitalMarkLane",
                    "You definitely have a great Rank Tracker 🥳👏"
                )
        .features
          .features__container
            .feaures__backgound
              .features__item
                h2 Track, Report, Update: All-in-One
                p Experience a new level of rank tracking with daily updates, </br>  white-label reports, real-time alerts, and more
              .features__list
                +featureItem(
                  "img/dailyTracking@2x.webp",
                  "Daily Tracking",
                  "Your SERP Tracker will update your keyword positions every 24 hours, ensuring the data you see is always up-to-date. On your dashboard, you'll find the latest results as well as an archive of your past performances."
                )
                +featureItem(
                  "img/reporting@2x.webp",
                  "White-Label Reporting",
                  "Create instant reports or opt for automatic delivery to your inbox daily, weekly, or monthly. Need to present reports to your clients? Customize them with your logo and company colors, providing a professional and personalized touch."
                )
                +featureItem(
                  "img/onDemand@2x.webp",
                  "On-Demand Updates",
                  "Your keyword tracker automatically updates daily so that your data is accurate and timely. Need fresh-out-the-oven rankings? You can refresh your rank tracker on-demand, as often as you'd like."
                )
                +featureItem(
                  "img/localTracking@2x.webp",
                  "Local Tracking",
                  "Full local SEO support allowing you to choose a country-specific Google domain, search from a specific geo-location, and include Local Map Pack in your results."
                )
                +featureItem(
                  "img/customAlerts@2x.webp",
                  "Custom Alerts",
                  'Stay proactive with our "Custom Alerts" feature. This tool sends an email alert when specified changes occur in your rankings, allowing you to react promptly to fluctuations in your SEO performance.'
                )
                +featureItem(
                  "img/api@2x.webp",
                  "API",
                  "Leverage the power of our Rank Tracker API for seamless integration and interaction with your existing systems. It offers real-time access to your keyword rankings data, enabling programmatic queries and allowing you to embed the insights into your own applications or workflows."
                )


              

            
            
          
          

      

          
